OL,3,CGen Zs quitting banking jobs for
OL,4,C'entrepreneurial experiences', bosses
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FGen Z workers are increasingly walking
OL,8,Faway from banking jobs in pursuit of
OL,9,Fentrepreneurial opportunities or more
OL,10,Fflexible working, a new survey of
OL,11,Fsenior bosses has found.
OL,13,FMost financial firms are taking action
OL,14,Fin a bid to hold onto their younger
OL,15,Fmembers of staff.
OL,17,FNearly half of financial services
OL,18,Fleaders report an increase in Gen Z
OL,19,Femployees leaving their organisation
OL,20,Fover the past year, according to
OL,21,Fpolling by KPMG.
