OL,3,CGen Zs quitting banking jobs for
OL,4,C'entrepreneurial experiences', bosses
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThis rises to 54% of those within the
OL,8,Fbanking sector who noticed an upsurge.
OL,10,FGen Z ` typically referring to people
OL,11,Fborn between 1997 and 2012 ` are often
OL,12,Fseeking out more entrepreneurial-style
OL,13,Fwork in their decision to leave
OL,14,Ffinance jobs, the survey found.
OL,16,FThe biggest reason cited by the
OL,17,Ffinance bosses was a preference for
OL,18,Fworking in start-ups, at 42%.
