OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe poll, which was to around 150
OL,8,Fpeople at director level or above in
OL,9,Ffinancial services companies, found
OL,10,Fthat around a quarter of younger
OL,11,Femployees are estimated to have left
OL,12,Ffinance businesses in the past year.
OL,14,FAlmost all of the business leaders
OL,15,Fsurveyed, at 96%, said they were
OL,16,Ftaking active steps to try and improve
OL,17,FGen Z retention at their firm.
